<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Hi Raffaella<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I&#8217;ve attached a drop box link of documented it=
ems in your basement area, not including side closet yet.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Are you able to confirm for me if I can dispose thes=
e contents or if there is an item you see that you wish to retain.<o:p></o:=
p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
